rows.label: qev025904_MSG0002
rows.name:
This is the vessel bestowed upon me by our god,
Fortun. It is my true physical form.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025904_MSG0003
rows.name:
Stand and bear witness, Fraisie, to the power of the
Bringer of Miracles![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025904_MSG0004
rows.name: How...how can mere humans do this?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025904_MSG0005
rows.name:
Tch! I will not let this end here. Not this way.
...Mother Fortun, lend me your power![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025904_MSG0006
rows.name:
After her, [ST:playername ]!
If we don't stop her here, it it it will only lead to more
Fraisies in the future, won't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025904_MSG0007
rows.name:
Please bring this tragedy to an end, okay?
Avenge all the Ma-non they've slain, won't you?[ST:wait ]
